CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1781093477
OL,3,CEmma Raducanu starts grass season with
OL,4,Cconvincing Queen's win over Anna
OL,5,CBlinkova
OL,7,FIn May the 23-year-old, who has cycled
OL,8,Fthrough a steady stream of coaches
OL,9,Fsince winning the US Open as a 2021
OL,10,Fqualifier, rehired Andrew Richardson,
OL,11,Fwho had guided her to that triumph.
OL,13,FShe has also suffered from the
OL,14,Flingering impact of a post-viral
OL,15,Fillness, missing two and a half months
OL,16,Fof action before arriving in Paris,
OL,17,Fwhere she lost to Solana Sierra.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
