PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1781093477
OL,3,CEmma Raducanu starts grass season with
OL,4,Cconvincing Queen's win over Anna
OL,5,CBlinkova
OL,7,FThe Russian upped her game in the
OL,8,Fsecond set, breaking Raducanu twice as
OL,9,Fthe British number one began to
OL,10,Fstruggle with her serve, but
OL,11,FBlinkova's own difficulties returning
OL,12,Fsoon put Raducanu in the position of
OL,13,Fserving for the match, and she wrapped
OL,14,Fup the win less than an hour after it
OL,15,Fstarted.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/4
